Right now, your journey.

0:16:25.000,0:16:28.520
God owns our future.

0:16:28.520,0:16:40.180
Ask God to give you the grace to continue the journey - journey of righteousness,

0:16:40.180,0:16:44.840
purity, holiness, faithfulness.

0:16:44.840,0:16:56.920
Ask God for the grace to be kind to those who hurt you.

0:16:56.920,0:17:02.360
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:17:02.360,0:17:11.260
Ask for the grace.

